  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK667">
<l>uruvukaṇ ṭeḷḷāmai vēṇṭumuruḷ peruntērk</l>
<l>kaccāṇi yaṉṉā ruṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let none be despised for (their) size (for) the world has those who resemble the linch-pin of the big rolling car.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
